{"tid":2494782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企個MCB間歇性跳制","createTime":"2021-04-18T19:21:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T01:02:13.000Z","uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a16ad607226e395493d4c09255d5d5e6760562a4","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇巴打知跳制點搞<br />\n諗住試埋聽朝,搞唔掂再搵師傅<br />\n屋企大功率同設計簡單果D電器差唔多試曬<br />\n(不過蚊完都未解決到個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n呢家試淨電腦同差手機果D火牛<br />\n講多少少測試果陣，除非一啪個掣就即刻熄，如果唔係部電腦都著緊（趕緊功課），之後頂到一陣(大約45mins-3hours)，之後就會再跳<br />\n以我理解如果跳制關電腦事，都要過一段時間先會跳，所以點先知道跳掣係關電腦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMCB跳掣嗰粒係插蘇掣"},{"pid":"26a252625be01e1cf63a721b7a0e4b06536d389d","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a16ad607226e395493d4c09255d5d5e6760562a4","tid":2494782,"uid":311579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:21:49.000Z","msg":"想問下有冇巴打知跳制點搞<br />\n諗住試埋聽朝,搞唔掂再搵師傅<br />\n屋企大功率同設計簡單果D電器差唔多試曬<br />\n(不過蚊完都未解決到個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n呢家試淨電腦同差手機果D火牛<br />\n講多少少測試果陣，除非一啪個掣就即刻熄，如果唔係部電腦都著緊（趕緊功課），之後頂到一陣(大約45mins-3hours)，之後就會再跳<br />\n以我理解如果跳制關電腦事，都要過一段時間先會跳，所以點先知道跳掣係關電腦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMCB跳掣嗰粒係插蘇掣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T19:25:56.000Z","msg":"同埋MCB用左30年未換過